{"tid":928094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國駐港總領事稱避免政治審查十分重要","createTime":"2018-12-04T14:54:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-08T07:24:15.000Z","uid":51271,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"12395223d3ebfc77fc5b1e28c5c38afa0bdd2530","tid":928094,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T14:54:53.000Z","msg":"美國駐港總領事唐偉康接受本台電視節目《視點31》專訪，被問到立法會議員朱凱廸參選村代表提名無效的事件。唐偉康表示不願評論個別個案，但一般而言避免政治審查是十分重要，又認為市民擁護其政治主張，為香港帶來活力並變得特別。<br />\n<br />\n唐偉康又談及中美貿易談判，認為中國同意就保護知識產權、投資限制等方面對話，是向好的方面進發，又說對話不是要定輸贏，不認為美國是中美協議的贏家。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，香港和中美都有深厚的經濟關係，理解香港人對貿易戰感到焦慮。他認為香港擁有法治、獨立司法系統、保護知識產權、政府廉潔和可靠，外來者在香港有公平機會競爭，可以作為良好營商的例子。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1431710-20181204.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1431710-20181204.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=PVI6hBKaofi%2BzSQIbQ7rMMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=50b2860f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1431710-20181204.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=30488f09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1431710-20181204.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"2d654326eb5dc8d089f56e30505335e9e0a85c3f","tid":928094,"uid":92301,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T18:04:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90b3918c36f820eedd1267ecf6d008bcc86841ac","tid":928094,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T18:06:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"148865aa9833ff451a475659d9f98dc1865d2f58","tid":928094,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T20:21:00.000Z","msg":"政府廉潔和可靠"},{"pid":"b6818072f4493dc143415069bff11923bd8e1fbc","tid":928094,"uid":4783,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T20:23:16.000Z","msg":"職業外交官既官式說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連post出黎既必要都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46f7481a05b9e8745d9d8f592098637cafe6b002","tid":928094,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T07:24:15.000Z","msg":"."}]}